00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:21,320
You can't give up.

500
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:24,520
Jiang Jiang?

501
00:36:25,940 --> 00:36:28,980
I think Dr. Fang will achieve great things in the future.

502
00:36:28,980 --> 00:36:33,520
Because he knows where his problems are and he's thinking of solutions every day.

503
00:36:33,520 --> 00:36:39,880
Unlike some doctors who can only envy others' abilities and give up at the slightest difficulty.

504
00:36:40,500 --> 00:36:42,260
Read more biographies of famous people.

505
00:36:42,260 --> 00:36:45,420
How many people peak early in their careers only to end up with nothing?

506
00:36:45,420 --> 00:36:47,140
And how many people find success in their later years?

507
00:36:47,140 --> 00:36:48,920
Dr. Fang is definitely the latter.

508
00:36:48,920 --> 00:36:52,000
I hope you, Doctor, are not the former.

509
00:36:53,220 --> 00:36:57,720
Is she your friend? What a sharp tongue.

510
00:36:58,940 --> 00:37:00,640
Just ignore him.

511
00:37:00,640 --> 00:37:03,080
Thank you, Jiang Jiang.

512
00:37:03,080 --> 00:37:07,460
If anyone dares to stop you from trying, I'll teach them a proper lesson.

513
00:37:07,460 --> 00:37:09,320
Okay.

514
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:11,200
Go ahead.

515
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:35,540
Come in.

516
00:37:39,080 --> 00:37:41,120
Why are you here again?

517
00:37:42,940 --> 00:37:44,640
You tell me.

518
00:37:48,560 --> 00:37:50,160
What's the matter?

519
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:54,220
It's too stuffy in here. Let's eat outside.

520
00:37:54,220 --> 00:37:56,320
Eat outside?

521
00:37:57,200 --> 00:37:58,920
Are you sure?

522
00:37:58,920 --> 00:38:00,720
Yes.

523
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:06,820
Here.

524
00:38:08,260 --> 00:38:10,060
Eat some more.

525
00:38:17,960 --> 00:38:22,800
 If I knew people would stare at me like a national treasure when I ate outside, I would've just eaten inside.

526
00:38:24,420 --> 00:38:26,080
Just focus on eating.

527
00:38:26,080 --> 00:38:28,140
Don't worry about them.

528
00:38:28,140 --> 00:38:30,960
If you ignore them, they'll disperse on their own.

529
00:38:35,140 --> 00:38:37,660
Is there something on my face?

530
00:38:38,400 --> 00:38:42,400
The way you eat hasn't changed at all.

531
00:38:51,520 --> 00:38:55,640
Once you develop a habit, it's tough to change it.

532
00:38:56,620 --> 00:39:00,260
No matter how hard you try to pretend, it won't work.

533
00:39:00,260 --> 00:39:03,160
Why do I get criticized even when I'm eating?

534
00:39:03,160 --> 00:39:05,040
I'm full.

535
00:39:09,420 --> 00:39:12,020
Okay, I won't say any more.

536
00:39:12,020 --> 00:39:13,740
You've been working hard caring for the patient.

537
00:39:13,740 --> 00:39:15,540
Eat some more.

538
00:39:17,320 --> 00:39:19,120
Su Wei'an,

539
00:39:21,500 --> 00:39:26,160
- why on earth would you— 
 - If you keep asking questions, I'm going to be full again.

540
00:39:27,020 --> 00:39:29,740
Okay, I'll stop.

541
00:39:29,740 --> 00:39:31,040
I won't force you.

542
00:39:31,040 --> 00:39:36,560
But if you want to tell me one day, I'm always ready.

543
00:40:09,020 --> 00:40:11,440
