545
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:34,220

546
00:40:39,620 --> 00:40:43,940
 Wen Ran, you're actually tracking me.

547
00:40:50,920 --> 00:40:53,740
Yuncheng, you rarely ask me out.

548
