We haven't had a date like this in a long time.

549
00:41:00,900 --> 00:41:03,160
Let's break up.

550
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:12,900
Yuncheng, you're joking, right?

551
00:41:12,900 --> 00:41:19,260
For so many years, I've been trying to convince myself that you're my best choice.

552
00:41:19,260 --> 00:41:24,560
Although it's not a perfect match, at least we were happy together.

553
00:41:24,560 --> 00:41:29,440
But now I've realized that we're not people of the same world.

554
00:41:31,020 --> 00:41:34,960
Don't we have a lot in common?

555
00:41:36,920 --> 00:41:40,780
Yuncheng, if there's anything I didn't do well enough, just tell me.

556
00:41:40,780 --> 00:41:42,060
I can always improve.

557
00:41:42,060 --> 00:41:45,360
From the very beginning, we weren't a good fit.

558
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:47,280
I'm sorry.

559
